quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  11,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  11,1,"a l- ray farmaan hai, jis ki ayatain pukhta aur mufasil irshad hui hain, aik Dana aur bakhabar hasti ki taraf se"
  11,2,ke tum bandagi nah karo magar sirf Allah ki mein uss ki taraf se tum ko khabardaar karne wala bhi hon aur basharat dainay wala bhi
  11,3,aur yeh ke tum apne rab se maffi chaho aur is ki taraf palat aao to woh aik muddat khaas taq tum ko acha samaan zindagi day ga aur har sahib fazl ko is ka fazl ataa kere ga lekin agar tum mun phertey ho to mein tumahray haq mein aik barray holnaak din ke azaab se darta hon
  11,4,tum sab ko Allah ki taraf palatna hai aur woh sab kuch karsaktha hai
  11,5,"dekho! yeh log apne seenon ko morty hain taakay is se choup jayen khabardaar! jab yeh kapron se apne aap ko dhanpte hain, Allah un ke chupay ko bhi jaanta hai aur khulay ko bhi, woh to unn bheidoon se bhi waaqif hai jo seenon mein hain"
  11,6,"zameen mein chalne wala koi jandaar aisa nahi hai jis ka rizaq Allah ke zimmay nah ho aur jis ke mutaliq woh nah jaanta ho ke kahan woh rehta hai aur kahan woh sonpa jata hai, sab kuch aik saaf daftar mein darj hai"
  11,7,"aur wohi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay dinon mein peda kya jabkay is se pehlay is ka arsh pani par tha taakay tum ko aazma kar dekhe tum mein kon behtar amal karne wala hai ab agar ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum kehte ho ke logo, marnay ke baad tum dobarah uthaye jao ge, to munkareen foran bol uthte hain ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo giri hai"
  11,8,aur agar hum aik khaas muddat taq un ki saza ko talte hain to woh kehnay lagtay hain ke aakhir kis cheez ne ussay rok rakha hai? suno! jis roz uss saza ka waqt agaya to woh kisi ke phairay nah phir sakay ga aur wohi cheez un ko aa ghairay gi jis ka woh mazaq ura rahay hain
  11,9,agar kabhi hum ensaan ko apni rehmat se nawazne ke baad phir is se mahroom kar dete hain to woh mayoos hota hai aur nashukri karne lagta hai
  11,10,"aur agar uss museebat ke baad jo uss par aayi thi hum usay Nemat ka maza chukhatay hain to kehta hai mere to saaray dldr paar ho gay, phir woh phoola nahi samata aur akarnay lagta hai"
  11,11,is aib se pak agar koi hain to bas woh log jo sabr karne walay aur naiko car hain aur wohi hain jin ke liye dar guzar bhi hai aur bara ajar bhi
  11,12,"to aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam kahin aisa nah ho ke tum unn cheezon mein se kisi cheez ko ( bayan kar ne se ) chore do jo tumhari taraf wahi ki ja rahi hain aur iss baat par dil tang ho ke woh kahin ge"" is shakhs par koi khazana kyun nah utaara gaya"" ya yeh ke"" is ke sath koi farishta kyun nah aaya"" tum to mehez khabardaar karne walay ho, agay har cheez ka hawala daar Allah hai"
  11,13,"kya yeh kehte hain ke paighambar ne yeh kitaab khud ghurr li hai? kaho,"" acha yeh baat hai to is jaisi gharri hui das sortain tum bana lao aur Allah ke siwa aur jo jo ( tumahray mabood ) hain unn ko madad ke liye bulaa satke ho to bulaa lau agar tum ( inhen mabood samajhney mein ) sachey ho"
  11,14,"ab agar woh ( tumahray mabood ) tumhari madad ko nahi pahunchte to jaan lau ke yeh Allah ke ilm se nazil hui hai aur yeh ke Allah ke siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahi hai phir kya tum ( is amar haq ke agay ) sir tasleem khham kar te ho? """
  11,15,jo log bas isi duniya ki zindagi aur is ki khooshnumayoon ke taalib hotay hain un ki car guzari ka sara phal hum yahin un ko day dete hain aur is mein un ke sath koi kami nahi ki jati
  11,16,magar akhirat mein aisay logon ke liye aag ke siwa kuch nahi hai ( wahan maloom ho jaye ga ke ) jo kuch unhon ne duniya mein banaya woh sab malyamait ho gaya aur ab un ka sara kya dhara mehez baatil hai
  11,17,"phir bhala woh shakhs jo apne rab ki taraf se aik saaf shahadat rakhta tha, is ke baad aik gawah bhi parvar-digaar ki taraf se ( is shahadat ki taied mein ) aa gaya, aur pehlay moose ki kitaab rehnuma aur rehmat ke tor par aayi hui bhi mojood thi ( kya woh bhi duniya paraston ki terhan is se inkaar karsaktha hai? ) aisay log to is par imaan hi layein ge aur insani garohoon mein se jo koi is ka inkaar kere to is ke liye jis jagah ka wada hai woh dozakh hai pas ae Peghambar tum iss cheez ki taraf se kisi shak mein nah parna, yeh haq hai tumahray rab ki taraf se magar aksar log nahi mantay"
  11,18,aur uss shakhs se barh kar zalim aur kon hoga jo Allah par jhoot gharrey? aisay log apne rab ke huzoor paish hon ge aur gawah shahadat den ge ke yeh hain woh log jinhon ne apne rab par jhoot ghara tha suno! khuda ki laanat hai zaalmon par
  11,19,"unn zaalmon par jo khuda ke rastay se logon ko roktay hain, is ke rastay ko ٹیٹرھا karna chahtay hain aur akhirat ka inkaar karte hain"
  11,20,woh zameen mein Allah ko be bas karne walay nah thay aur nah Allah ke muqaabla mein koi un ka haami tha inhen ab dohra azaab diya jaye ga woh nah kisi ki sun hi satke thay aur nah khud hi inhen kuch sujhta tha
  11,21,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne apne aap ko khud ghatay mein dala aur woh sab kuch un se khoya gaya jo unhon ne ghurr rakha tha
  11,22,na Guzir hai ke wohi akhirat mein sab se barh kar ghatay mein rahen
  11,23,"rahay woh log jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye aur apne rab hi ke ho kar rahay, to yaqeenan woh janati log hain aur jannat mein woh hamesha rahen ge"
  11,24,"inn dono fareeqon ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik aadmi to ho andha berha aur dosra ho dekhnay aur suneney wala, kya yeh dono yaksaa ho satke hain? kya tum ( iss misaal se ) koi sabaq nahi letay ?"
  11,25,"( aur aisay hi halaat thay jab ) hum ne Nooh ko uss ki qoum ki taraf bheja tha ( uss ne kaha )"" mein tum logon ko saaf saaf khabardaar karta hon"
  11,26,"ke Allah ke siwa kisi ki bandagi nah karo warna mujhe andesha hai ke tum par aik roz dard naak azaab aeye ga """
  11,27,"jawab mein uss ki qoum ke sardar, jinhon ne is ki baat maan-ne se inkaar kya tha, bolay"" hamari nazar mein to tum is ke siwa kuch nahi ho ke bas aik ensaan ho hum jaisay aur hum dekh rahay hain ke hamari qoum mein se bas unn logon ne jo hamaray haan اrazil )kamtar) thay be soochey samjhay tumhari pairwi ikhtiyar kar li hai aur hum koi cheez bhi aisi nahi paate jis mein tum log hum se kuch barhay hue ho, balkay hum to tumhe jhoota samajte hain """
  11,28,"is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, zara socho to sahi ke agar mein apne rab ki taraf se aik khuli shahadat par qaim tha aur phir is ne mujh ko apni khaas rehmat se bhi Nawaz diya magar woh tum ko nazar nah aayi to aakhir hamaray paas kya zareya hai ke tum maanna nah chaho aur hum zabardasti is ko tumahray sir chipka den ?"
  11,29,"aur ae baradran qoum, mein iss kaam par tum se koi maal nahi mangta, mera ajar to Allah ke zimma hai aur mein unn logon ko dhakkay dainay se bhi raha jinhon ne meri baat maani hai, woh aap hi apne rab ke huzoor jaane walay hain magar mein daikhta hon ke tum log jahalat bart rahay ho"
  11,30,"aur ae qoum, agar mein inn logon ko dhtkar dun to khuda ki pakar se kon mujhe bachanay aeye ga? tum logon ki samajh mein kya itni baat bhi nahi aati ?"
  11,31,"aur mein tum se nahi kehta ke mere paas Allah ke khazanay hain, nah yeh kehta hon ke mein ghaib ka ilm rakhta hon, nah yeh mera daawa hai ke mein farishta hon aur yeh bhi mein nahi keh sakta ke jin logon ko tumhari ankhen hiqarat se dekhatii hain inhen Allah ne koi bhalai nahi di un ke nafs ka haal Allah hi behtar jaanta hai agar mein aisa kahoon to zalim hon ga """
  11,32,"aakhir-kaar un logon ne kaha ke"" ae Nooh, tum ne hum se jhagra kya aur bohat kar liya ab to bas woh azaab le aao jis ki tum hamein dhamki dete ho agar sachey ho """
  11,33,"Nooh ne jawab diya"" woh to Allah hi laaye ga, agar chahay ga, aur tum itna bil bota nahi rakhtay ke usay rok do"
  11,34,"ab agar mein tumhari kuch kher khawahi karna bhi chahoon to meri kher khawahi tumhe koi faida nahi day sakti jabkay Allah hi ne tumhe bhatka dainay ka iradah kar liya ho, wohi tumhara rab hai aur usi ki taraf tumhe palatna hai """
  11,35,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kya yeh log kehte hain ke iss shakhs ne yeh sab kuch khud ghurr liya hai? un se kaho"" agar mein ne yeh khud ghara hai to mujh par apne jurm ki zimma daari hai, aur jo jurm tum kar rahay ho is ki zimma daari se mein buri hon """
  11,36,"Nooh par wahi ki gayi ke tumhari qoum mein se jo log imaan laa chuke bas woh laa chuke, ab koi maan-ne wala nahi hai un ke krtoton par gham khana chhorro"
  11,37,"aur hamari nigrani mein hamari wahi ke mutabiq aik kashti banani shuru kar do aur dekho, jin logon ne zulm kya hai unn ke haq mein mujh se koi sifarish nah karna, yeh saaray ke saaray ab doobnay walay hain"
  11,38,"Nooh kashti bana raha tha aur is ki qoum ke sardaro mein se jo koi is ke paas se guzarta tha woh is ka mazaq urata tha is ne kaha"" agar tum hum par hanstay ho to hum bhi tum par hans rahay hain"
  11,39,"anqareeb tumhe khud maloom ho jaye ga ke kis par woh azaab aata hai jo ussay ruswa kar day ga aur kis par woh bulaa toot padtee hai jo talaay nah talle gi """
  11,40,"yahan taq ke jab hamara hukum agaya aur woh tano ray ubal para to hum ne kaha"" har qisam ke janwaron ka aik aik jora kashti mein rakh lau, apne ghar walon ko bhi siwaye unn ashkhaas ke jin ki nishaan dahi pehlay ki ja chuki hai is mein sawaar kara do aur un logon ko bhi bitha lau jo imaan laaye hain"" aur thoray hi log thay jo Nooh ke sath imaan laaye thay"
  11,41,"Nooh ne kaha"" sawaar ho jao iss mein, Allah hi ke naam se hai is ka chalna bhi aur is ka therna bhi, mera rab bara ghafoor o Raheem hai """
  11,42,"kashti un logon ko liye chali ja rahi thi aur aik aik mouj pahar ki terhan uth rahi thi Nooh ka beta daur faaslay par tha Nooh ne pukaar kar kaha"" beta, hamaray sath sawaar ho ja, kafiroon ke sath nah reh """
  11,43,"uss ne palat kar jawab diya"" mein abhi aik pahar par charha jata hon jo mujhe pani se bacha le ga"" Nooh ne kaha, aaj koi cheez Allah ke hukum se bachanay wali nahi hai siwaye iss ke ke Allah hi kisi par reham farmaiye"" itnay mein aik mouj dono ke darmain haail ho gayi aur woh bhi doobnay walon mein shaamil ho gaya"
  11,44,"hukum howa"" ae zameen, apna sara pani nigal ja aur ae aasman, ruk ja"" chunancha pani zameen mein baith gaya, faisla chuka diya gaya, kashti Jodi par tik gayi, aur keh diya gaya ke daur hui zaalmon ki qoum !"
  11,45,"Nooh ne apne rab ko puraka kaha"" ae rab, mera beta mere ghar walon mein se hai aur tera wada sacha hai aur to sab hakmon se bara aur behtar haakim hai """
  11,46,"jawab mein irshad howa"" ae Nooh, woh tairay ghar walon mein se nahi hai, woh to aik bigra howa kaam hai, lehaza to uss baat ki mujh se darkhwast nah kar jis ki haqeeqat to nahi jaanta, mein tujhe nasiyaat karta hon ke apne aap ko jahilon ki terhan nah bana le """
  11,47,"Nooh ne foran arz kya"" ae mere rab, mein teri panah mangta hon iss se ke woh cheez tujh se maanguu jis ka mujhe ilm nahi agar to ne mujh maaf nah kya aur reham nah farmaya to mein barbaad ho jaoon ga """
  11,48,"hukum howa"" ae Nooh utar ja, hamari taraf se salamti aur barkaten hain tujh par aur un garohoon par jo tairay sath hain, aur kuch giroh aisay bhi hain jin ko hum kuch muddat samaan zindagi bakhsheen ge phir inhen hamari taraf se dard naak azaab puhanche ga """
  11,49,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh ghaib ki khabrain hain jo hum tumhari taraf wahi kar rahay hain is se pehlay nah tum un ko jantay thay aur nah tumhari qoum, pas sabr karo, a Najjan car Muttaqiyun hi ke haq mein hai"
  11,50,"aur Aad ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai hood ko bheja uss ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, Allah ki bandagi karo, tumhara koi khuda uss ke siwa nahi hai tum ne mehez jhoot ghurr rakhay hain"
  11,51,"ae baradran qoum, is kaam par mein tum se koi ajar nahi chahta, mera ajar to is ke zimma hai jis ne mujhe peda kya hai, kya tum aqal se zara kaam nahi letay ?"
  11,52,"aur ae meri qoum ke logo, apne rab se maffi chaho, phir is ki taraf paltoo, woh tum par aasman ke dhanay khol day ga aur tumhari mojooda qowat par mazeed qowat ka izafah kere ga mujrimon ki terhan mun nah phero """
  11,53,"unhon ne jawab diya"" ae hood, to hamaray paas koi Sarih shahadat le kar nahi aaya hai, aur tairay kehnay se hum apne mabodon ko nahi chore satke, aur tujh par hum imaan laane walay nahi hain"
  11,54,"hum to yeh samajte hain ke tairay oopar hamaray mabodon mein se kisi ki maar par gayi hai"" hood ne kaha"" mein Allah ki shahadat paish karta hon aur tum gawah raho ke yeh jo Allah ke siwa dosaron ko tum ne khudai mein shareektehra rakha hai is se mein bezaar hon"
  11,55,tum sab ke sab mil kar mere khilaaf apni karni mein kasar nah utha rakho aur mujhe zara mohlat nah do
  11,56,mera bharosa Allah par hai jo mera rab bhi hai aur tumhara rab bhi koi jandaar aisa nahi jis ki chouti is ke haath mein nah ho be shak mera rab seedhi ray ah par hai
  11,57,"agar tum mun phertey ho to phair lau jo pegham day kar mein tumahray paas bheja gaya tha woh mein tum ko pouncha chuka hon ab mera rab tumhari jagah doosri qoum ko uthaye ga aur tum is ka kuch nah bigaar sakuu ge yaqeenan mera rab har cheez par nigaran hai """
  11,58,phir jab hamara hukum agaya to hum ne apni rehmat se hood ko aur unn logon ko jo uss ke sath imaan laaye thay nijaat day di aur aik sakht azaab se bacha liya
  11,59,"yeh hain Aad , apne rab ki ayaat se unhon ne inkaar kya, is ke Rasolo-n ki baat nah maani, aur har Jabbar dushman haq ki pairwi karte rahay"
  11,60,"aakhir-kaar is duniya mein bhi un par phatkaar pari aur qayamat ke roz bhi suno! Aad ne apne rab se kufar kya, suno! daur pheink diye gay Aad , hood ki qoum ke log"
  11,61,"aur smod ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai saleh ko bheja uss ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, Allah ki bandagi karo, aُ seen ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai wohi hai jis ne tum ko zameen se peda kya hai aur yahan tum ko basaayaa hai lehaza tum is se maffi chaho aur is ki taraf palat aao, yaqeenan mera rab qareeb hai aur woh duaon ka jawab dainay wala hai """
  11,62,"unhon ne kaha"" ae saleh, is se pehlay to hamaray darmain aisa shakhs tha jis se barri tawaquaat wabsta theen kya to hamein un mabodon ki parastish se rokna chahta hai jin ki parastish hamaray baap dada karte thay? to jis tareeqay ki taraf hamein bulaa raha hai is ke baray mein hum ko sakht shuba hai jis ne hamein Khuljan mein daal rakha hai """
  11,63,"saleh ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, tum ne kuch is baat par bhi ghhor kya ke agar mein apne rab ki taraf se aik saaf shahadat rakhta tha, aur phir is ne apni rehmat se bhi mujh ko Nawaz diya to iss ke baad Allah ki pakar se mujhe kon bachaaye ga agar mein uss ki nafarmani karoon? tum mere kis kaam aa satke ho siwaye is ke ke mujhe aur ziyada khasaray mein daal do"
  11,64,"aur ae meri qoum ke logo, dekho yeh Allah ki oontni tumahray liye aik nishani hai isay khuda ki zameen mein charnay ke liye azad chore do iss se zara tarruz nah karna warna kuch ziyada der nah guzray gi ke tum par khuda ka azaab aa jaye ga """
  11,65,"magar unhon ne oontni ko maar dala is par saleh ne unn ko khabardaar kar diya ke"" bas ab teen din apne gharon mein aur reh bas lau yeh aisi meyaad hai jo jhooti nah saabit hogi """
  11,66,aakhir-kaar jab hamaray faislay ka waqt aa gaya to hum ne apni rehmat se saleh ko aur unn logon ko jo is ke sath imaan laaye thay bacha liya aur uss din ki ruswai se un ko mehfooz rakha be shak tera rab hi darasal taaqatwar aur baala dast hai
  11,67,rahay woh log jinhon ne zulm kya tha to aik sakht dhamakay ne un ko dhar liya aur woh apni bustiyon mein is terhan be hiss o harkat parre ke parre reh gay
  11,68,ke goya woh wahan kabhi basey hi nah thay suno! smod ne apne rab se kufar kya suno! daur pheink diye gay smod !
  11,69,"aur dekho, ibrahim ke paas hamaray farishtay khushkhabri liye hue puhanche kaha tum par salam ho ibrahim ne jawab diya tum par bhi salam ho phir kuch der nah guzri ke ibrahim aik bhana howa bitchrha ( un ki ziyafat ke liye ) le aaya"
  11,70,"magar jab dekha ke un ke haath khanay par nahi barhatay to woh un se mushtaba ho gaya aur dil mein un se khauf mehsoos karne laga onhon ne kaha"" daro nahi, hum to loot ki qoum ki taraf beje gay hain """
  11,71,ibrahim ki biwi bhi khari hui thi woh yeh sun kar hans di phir hum ne is ko ishaq ki aur ishaq ke baad Yaqoob ki khushkhabri di
  11,72,"woh boli"" haae meri kam bakhti! kya ab mere haan aulaad hogi jabkay mein budiya phons ho gayi aur yeh mere miyan bhi boorhay ho chuke? yeh to barri ajeeb baat hai """
  11,73,"firshton ne kaha"" Allah ke hukum par taajjub karti ho? ibrahim ke ghar walo, tum logon par to Allah ki rehmat aur uss ki barkaten hain, aur yaqeenan Allah nihayat qabil tareef aur barri shaan wala hai """
  11,74,phir jab ibrahim ki ghabrahat daur ho gayi aur ( aulaad ki basharat se ) is ka dil khush ho gaya to is ne qoum Loot ke muamlay mein hum se jhagra shuru kya
  11,75,haqeeqat mein ibrahim bara Haleem aur naram dil aadmi tha aur har haal mein hamari taraf rujoo karta tha
  11,76,"( aakhir-kaar hamaray firshton ne is se kaha )"" ae ibrahim, is se baz aa jao, tumahray rab ka hukum ho chuka hai aur ab un logon par woh azaab aakar rahay ga jo kisi ke phairay nahi phir sakta """
  11,77,aur jab hamaray farishtay loot ke paas puhanche to unn ki aamad se woh bohat ghabraya aur dil tang howa aur kehnay laga ke aaj barri museebat ka din hai
  11,78,"( un mehmanon ka aana tha ke ) is ki qoum ke log be ikhtiyar is ke ghar ki taraf daud parre pehlay se woh aisi hi bad karyon ke khogar thay loot ne un se kaha"" bhayyo, yeh meri betiyan mojood hain, yeh tumahray liye pakeeza tar hain kuch khuda ka khauf karo aur mere mehmanon ke muamlay mein mujhe zaleel nah karo kya tum mein koi bhala aadmi nahi? """
  11,79,"unhon ne jawab diya"" tujhe to maloom hi hai ke teri baityon mein hamara koi hissa nahi hai aur to yeh bhi jaanta hai ke hum chahtay kya hain """
  11,80,"loot ne kaha"" kash mere paas itni taaqat hoti ke tumhe seedha kar deta, ya koi mazboot sahara hi hota ke is ki panah laita """
  11,81,"tab firshton ne is se kaha ke"" ae loot, hum tairay rab ke beje hue farishtay hain, yeh log tera kuch nah bigaar saken ge bas to kuch raat rahay apne ahal o Ayal ko le kar nikal ja aur dekho, tum mein se koi shakhs peechay palat kar nah dekhe magar teer y biwi ( sath nahi jaye gi ) kyunkay is par bhi wohi kuch guzarnay wala hai jo inn logon par guzarna hai un ki tabahi ke liye subah ka waqt muqarrar hai subah hotay ab der hi kitni hai! """
  11,82,phir jab hamaray faislay ka waqt aa pouncha to hum ne is bastii ko tall patt kar diya aur is par paki hui matti ke pathar tabrh toar barsaye
  11,83,jin mein se har pathar tairay rab ke haan nishaan zada tha aur zaalmon se yeh saza kuch daur nahi hai
  11,84,"aur Mudin walon ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai Shoiab ko bheja uss ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, Allah ki bandagi karo, is ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai aur naap toal mein kami nah kya karo aaj mein tum ko achay haal mein dekh raha hon, magar mujhe dar hai ke kal tum par aisa din aeye ga jis ka azaab sab ko ghair le ga"
  11,85,"aur ae baradran qoum, theek theek insaaf ke sath poora ناپو aur tulo aur logon ko un ki cheezon mein ghata nah diya karo aur zameen mein fasaad nah pheilatay phiro"
  11,86,"Allah ki di hui bachat tumahray liye behtar hai agar tum momin ho aur bahar haal mein tumahray oopar koi nigran car nahi hon """
  11,87,"unhon ne jawab diya"" ae Shoiab, kya teri namaz tujhe yeh sikhati hai ke hum un saaray mabodon ko chore den jin ki par- satish hamaray baap dada karte thay? ya yeh ke hum ko apne maal mein apne Mansha ke mutabiq tasarruf karne ka ikhtiyar nah ho? bas to hi to aik aliiiii zarf aurrasbaaz aadmi reh gaya hai! """
  11,88,"Shoiab ne kaha"" bhayyo, tum khud hi socho ke agar mein apne rab ki taraf se aik khuli shahadat par tha aur phir is ne apne haan se mujh ko acha rizaq bhi ataa kya ( to is ke baad mein tumhari gmrahyon aur haraam khoryunmein tumhara shareek haal kaisay ho sakta hon? ) aur mein hargiz yeh nahi chahta ke jin baton se mein tum ko rokta hon un ka khud irtikaab karoon mein to islaah karna chahta hon jahan taq bhi mera bas chalay aur yeh jo kuch mein karna chahta hon is ka sara inhisaar Allah ki tofeq par hai, usi par mein ne bharosa kya aur har maamla mein isi ki taraf mein rujoo karta hon"
  11,89,"aur ae baradran qoum, mere khilaaf tumhari hatt dharmi kahin yeh nobat nah pouncha day ke aakhir-kaar tum par bhi wohi azaab aa kar rahay jo Nooh ya hood ya saleh ki qoum par aaya tha aur loot ki qoum to tum se kuch ziyada daur bhi nahi hai"
  11,90,"dekho! apne rab se maffi mango aur is ki taraf palat aao, be shak mera rab Raheem hai aur apni makhlooq se mohabbat rakhta hai """
  11,91,"unhon ne jawab diya"" ae Shoiab, teri bohat si baatein to hamari samajh hi mein nahi aatin aur hum dekhte hain ke to hamaray darmain aik be zor aadmi hai, teri baradri nah hoti to hum kabhi ka tujhe sangsar kar chuke hotay, tera bil bota to itna nahi hai ke hum par bhaari ho """
  11,92,"Shoiab ne kaha"" bhayyo, kya meri baradri tum par Allah se ziyada bhaari hai ke tum ne ( baradri ka to khauf kya aur ) Allah ko bilkul pas pusht daal diya? jaan rakho ke jo kuch tum kar rahay ho woh Allah ki girift se bahar nahi hai"
  11,93,"ae meri qoum ke logo, tum apne tareeqay par kaam kiye jao aur mein apne tareeqay par karta rahon ga, jaldi hi tumhe maloom ho jaye ga ke kis par zillat ka azaab aata hai aur kon jhoota hai tum bhi intzaar karo aur mein bhi tumahray sath chasham barah hon """
  11,94,aakhir-kaar jab hamaray faislay ka waqt aa gaya to hum ne apni rehmat se Shoiab aur is ke saathi mominon ko bacha liya aur jin logon ne zulm kya tha un ko aik sakht dhamakay ne aisa pakra ke woh apni bustiyon mein be hiss o harkat parre ke parre reh gay
  11,95,goya woh kabhi wahan rahay basey hi nah thay suno! Mudin walay bhi daur pheink diye gay jis terhan smod phainky gay thay
  11,96,aur moose ko hum ne apni nshanyon aur khuli khuli sanad mamooriyat ke sath firaon aur is ke 'Ayanay (uhedaydar)saltanat ki taraf bheja
  11,97,magar unhon ne firaon ke hukum ki pairwi ki halaank firaon ka hukum raasti par nah tha
  11,98,qayamat ke roz woh apni qoum ke agay agay hoga aur apni peshwai mein inhen dozakh ki taraf le jaye ga kaisi badter jaye warood hai yeh jis par koi puhanche !
  11,99,aur un logon par duniya mein bhi laanat pari aur qayamat ke roz bhi parre gi kaisa bura sila hai yeh jo kisi ko miley !
  11,100,yeh chand bustiyon ki sarguzisht hai jo hum tumhe suna rahay hain un mein se baaz ab bhi khari hain aur baaz ki fasal kat chuki hai
  11,101,"hum ne unn par zulm nahi kya, unhon ne aap hi apne oopar sitam dhaya aur jab Allah ka hukum aa gaya to un ke woh mabood jinhein woh Allah ko chore kar puraka karte thay un ke kuch kaam nah aa sakay aur unhon ne halakat o barbadi ke siwa inhen kuch faida nah diya"
  11,102,"aur tera rab jab kisi zalim bastii ko pokarta hai to phir is ki pakar aisi hi howa karti hai, fi al waqea is ki pakar barri sakht aur dard naak hoti hai"
  11,103,haqeeqat yeh hai ke is mein aik nishani hai har uss shakhs ke liye jo azaab akhirat ka khauf kere woh aik din hoga jis mein sab log jama hon ge aur phir jo kuch bhi uss roz hoga sab ki aankhon ke samnay hoga
  11,104,"hum is ke laane mein kuch bohat ziyada takheer nahi kar rahay hain, bas aik gani chni muddat is ke liye muqarrar hai"
  11,105,"jab woh aeye ga to kisi ko baat karne ki majaal nah hogi, ila yeh ke khuda ki ijazat se kuch arz kere phir kuch log is roz bad bakht hon ge aur kuch naik bakht"
  11,106,jo bad bakht hon ge woh dozakh mein jayen ge ( jahan garmi aur pyaas ki shiddat se ) woh hanpain (sans phol jaye ga) ge aur phunkaraymarain ge
  11,107,"aur isi haalat mein woh hamesha rahen ge jab taq ke zameen o aasman qaim hain, ila yeh ke tera rab kuch aur chahay be shak tera rab poora ikhtiyar rakhta hai ke jo chahay kere"
  11,108,"rahay woh log jo naik bakht nikleen ge, to woh jannat mein jayen ge aur wahan hamesha rahen ge jab taq zameen o aasman qaim hain, ila yeh ke tera rab kuch aur chahay aisi bakhshish un ko miley gi jis ka silsila kabhi munqita nah hoga"
  11,109,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, to un mabodon ki taraf se kisi shak mein nah reh jin ki yeh log ibadat kar rahay hain yeh to ( bas lakeer ke faqeer banay hue ) usi terhan pooja paat kiye ja rahay hain jis terhan pehlay un ke baap dada karte thay, aur hum inn ka hissa aِnhin bharpoor den ge baghair is ke ke is mein kuch kaat kasar ho"
  11,110,hum is se pehlay moose ko bhi kitaab day chuke hain aur is ke baray mein bhi ikhtilaaf kya gaya tha ( jis terhan aaj iss kitaab ke baray mein kya ja raha hai jo tumhe di gayi hai ) agar tairay rab ki taraf se aik baat pehlay hi tey nah kar di gayi hoti to inn ikhtilaaf karne walon ke darmain kabhi ka faisla chuka diya gaya hota yeh waqea hai ke yeh log is ki taraf se shak aur Khuljan mein parre hue hain
  11,111,"aur yeh bhi waqea hai ke tera rab inhen un ke aamaal ka poora poora badla day kar rahay ga, yaqeenan woh un ki sab harkato se bakhabar hai"
  11,112,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum, aur tumahray woh saathi jo ( kufar o baghaawat se imaan o taat ki taraf ) palat aeye hain, theek theek raah raast par saabit qadam raho jaissa ke tumhe hukum diya gaya hai aur bandagi ki hadd se tajawaz nah karo jo kuch tum kar rahay ho is par tumhara rab nigah rakhta hai"
  11,113,inn zaalmon ki taraf zara nah jhukna warna jahannum ki lapait mein aa jao ge aur tumhe koi aisa walii o sarparast nah miley ga jo khuda se tumhe bacha sakay aur kahin se tum ko madad nah puhanche gi
  11,114,"aur dekho, namaz qaim karo din ke dono suron par aur kuch raat guzarnay par dar haqeeqat naikian buraiyon ko daur kar deti hain, yeh aik yaad dehani hai un logon ke liye jo khuda ko yaad rakhnay walay hain"
  11,115,"aur sabr kar, Allah neki karne walon ka ajar kabhi zaya nahi karta"
  11,116,"phir kyun nah unn qomon mein jo tum se pehlay guzar chuki hain aisay ahal kher mojood rahay jo logon ko zameen mein fasaad barpaa karne se roktay? aisay log niklay bhi to bohat kam, jin ko hum ne un qomon mein se bacha liya, warna zalim log to unhi mazonke peechay parre rahay jin ke samaan inhen farawani ke sath diye gay thay aur woh mujrim ban kar rahay"
  11,117,tera rab aisa nahi hai ke bustiyon ko na-haq tabah kar day halaank un ke bashinday islaah karne walay hon
  11,118,"be shak tera rab agar chahta to tamam insanon ko aik giroh bana sakta tha, magar ab to woh mukhtalif tareeqon hi par chaltay rahen ge"
  11,119,"aur be raah rawaiyon se sirf woh log bachchen ge jin par tairay rab ki rehmat hai isi ( azaadi intikhab o ikhtiyar ) ke liye hi to is ne inhen peda kya tha aur tairay rab ki woh baat poori ho gayi jo is ne kahi thi ke mein jahannum ko jin aur ensaan, sab se bhar dun ga"
  11,120,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh payghambaroon ke qissay jo hum tumhe sunaate hain, woh cheezein hain jin ke zariye se hum tumahray dil ko mazboot karte hain un ke andar tum ko haqeeqat ka ilm mila aur imaan laane walon ko nasiyaat aur baydaari naseeb hui"
  11,121,"rahay woh log jo imaan nahi laatay, to un se keh do ke tum apne tareeqay par kaam karte raho aur hum apne tareeqay par kiye jatay hain"
  11,122,injaam car ka tum bhi intzaar karo aur hum bhi muntazir hain
  11,123,"asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch chhupa howa hai sab Allah ke qabza qudrat mein hai aur sara maamla isi ki taraf rujoo kya jata hai pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, to is ki bandagi kar aur isi par bhrosa rakh, jo kuch tum log kar rahay ho tera rab is se be khabar nahi hai"
